      Help us! It's 2050 and the Earth is in grave danger.
 Greenhouse gas emissions have empowered two dangerous enemies:

                 Hurricanes and Forest Fires

Our enemies are attacking and we have no defenses to protect us!
 Thankfully, the Earth's citizens decided to help in the fight!
    You're equipped with three different types of bullets:

                  Compost, Diet, and Unplug

         Defeat the enemies until the time runs out!
            Press space to enter the fight . . .
